title: Fixed unexpected checking/unchecking of the CheckBox.
message:
Fixed unexpected checking/unchecking of the CheckBox.

When a CheckBox is reused, the event listener in it is kicked in
initializing. This patch avoids this bug to set the listener before
initializing state.
